variables.name: description
variables.comment: * A brief description of the property, which may be null.

variables.name: required
variables.comment: * The required field is true if a value must be * supplied for this property * during Driver.connect and false otherwise.

variables.name: value
variables.comment: * The value field specifies the current value of * the property, based on a combination of the information * supplied to the method getPropertyInfo, the * Java environment, and the driver-supplied default values. This field * may be null if no value is known.

variables.name: choices
variables.comment: * An array of possible values if the value for the field * DriverPropertyInfo.value may be selected * from a particular set of values; otherwise null.
